dct_title_s: Official Indiana : showing counties in different colors, townships, cities, villages, post offices, steam and electric railways with stations and distances between stations
dct_description_sm: Split into North and South Sheets. "Indiana combination edition no. 1324."  Includes "Index with populations according to 1930 federal census," population tables, distance chart, chart of land survey system, and inset showing "Congressional districts established 1931."  The same map overprinted with roads appears on verso.
Imprint: Indianapolis, Ind. : National Map Company, [c1931]
